OL,6,FA musician is bringing Welsh-language
OL,7,Fhymns that had previously been
OL,8,Fforgotten back to life after
OL,9,Fdiscovering them in a museum archive.
OL,11,FWelsh musician Lleuwen Steffan
OL,12,Fdiscovered the hymns in ' sound
OL,13,Farchive, with many of them dating back
OL,14,Fto the eighteenth century.
OL,16,FHowever, Lleuwen believes that the old
OL,17,Fhymns touch on contemporary issues
OL,18,Fsuch as mental health and alcoholism.
