OL,11,FMwynwen Mai Jones' grandfather
OL,12,Fperformed some of the hymns contained
OL,13,Fwithin the archive. She said: "It's a
OL,14,Fvery personal experience, religiously
OL,15,Fand also for the family.
OL,17,F"My daughters are here tonight- it's
OL,18,Fthe second time they're hearing the
OL,19,Fvoice of my grandfather. I see it as
