OL,6,FBacked by the National Eisteddfod,
OL,7,FLleuwen toured chapels across Wales to
OL,8,Fperform the hymns throughout February,
OL,9,FApril, and the start of May. She plans
OL,10,Fto perform the hymns again this summer.
OL,12,FBeti Wyn James is reverend of Capel Y
OL,13,FPriordy in , one of the chapels where
OL,14,FLleuwen performed the hymns.
OL,16,F"We live in a country with so many
OL,17,Frenowned hymn writers and their works
OL,18,Fhave been very influential on the
OL,19,Freligious lives of our nation," Rev
OL,20,FJames said.
